                        <p style="font-family:'Source Sans Pro'; font-size:1.3em; font-weight:800; line-height:22px; margin-bottom:20px;">Your child has begun “Monarch Butterfly” and has expressed<br />interest in becoming a Butterfly Hero by starting a milkweed garden<br />to help keep this important food source available for future<br />generations of this endangered species.</p>
                        <p style="font-family:'Source Sans Pro'; font-size:1.3em; font-weight:800; line-height:22px;">Our partner organization, National Wildlife Federation, is sponsoring<br />this free program. If you are interested in allowing your child<br />to participate you will need to provide an email and address to receive<br />a Butterfly Garden Starter Packet with seeds and information, stickers<br />and poster. Everything your child will need.<br />After you approve go to <a style="color:#3142a9;" href="http://www.nwf.org/butterflyheroes" target="_blank">www.nwf.org/butterflyheroes</a></p>
